      "title": "Re-Spawn Legendary Giants (Platinum)",
      "documentation": "This code resets the caught status of the legendary giants (Regirock, Regice and Registeel). In order to encounter them, you must still have a fateful encounter Regigigas in the party.\n\nThe first command resets Registeel, the second command resets Regice and the last command resets Regirock.",
